item.title: SoftLayer_Software_Component_ControlPanel_Cpanel
item.description: SoftLayer_Software_Component_ControlPanel_Cpanel Datatype Description This object specifies a specific Software Component: A cPanel instance. cPanel installations have a specific default port (2086) and a pattern for usernames and passwords. Defaults are initiated by this object. Local hardwareId Hardware Identification Number for the server this Software Component is installed upon. Type: integer id An ID number identifying this Software Component (Software Installation) Type: integer
